body:
Incorrect use of spreadsheets is a key challenge for data quality. Data that is not well managed cannot answer important questions or be used easily. Good management of data makes it easy to ensure data quality, and analyse and visualise results.

This course will enable you to organise spreadsheet data, use tools to filter & analyse data and produce an interactive data visualisation.
title: Foundations in data management
